# cp
    :"Copy", copy files & directories.
____________________________________

> cp [OPTION]... [SOURCE] [DESTINATION]

    [OPTION]
        -r, --recursive
            :recursively mode.

	    -v, --verbose
            :verbose mode

	    -i, --interactive
            :interactive mode	

	    -f, --force
            :force mode

	    -n, --no-clobber
            :no overwrite mode

	    -u
            :update mode


## EXAMPLES
    > cp -rv test/ /home/